request the distribution of tags used by.query:
PREFIX snvoc: <http://localhost:3000/www.ldbc.eu/ldbc_socialnet/1.0/vocabulary/>
PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>

SELECT ?tagName (COUNT(?message) AS ?messages)
WHERE {
  ?message snvoc:hasCreator <http://localhost:3000/pods/00000000000000000933/profile/card#me> ;
           snvoc:hasTopic ?tag .
  ?tag foaf:name ?tagName .
}
GROUP BY ?tagName
ORDER BY DESC(?messages)

request the distribution of tags used by.rules:
@prefix semmap: <https://semanticmapping.org/vocab#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>.
@prefix snvoc: <http://localhost:3000/www.ldbc.eu/ldbc_socialnet/1.0/vocabulary/>.

[]
    a semmap:RuleSet ;
    semmap:subweb "*" ;
    semmap:rule _:rule1 .

_:rule1
    semmap:premise snvoc:hasTag ;
    semmap:inference owl:equivalentProperty ;
    semmap:conclusion snvoc:hasTopic .

